#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:707
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[1]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"RADIKAL SHIP:\n"
"\t\t\tProbably dangerous, maybe also to itself and/or its crew.\n"
"\t\t\tProbably has lootable RadiKal gear: unlocks internal upgrades and RK sector blue options or coordinates."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:717
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[2]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"LEAD TITANS:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's Crystals, Lanius, Rockmen and Saltmen have: 2.5x resistance to everything, 2.5x damage to everything, they create breaches while walking, and can't repair.\n"
"\t\t\tThe other crew get a flat +75% repair speed.\n"
"\t\t\tAll of this ship's crew gain a flat +40% movement speed"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:726
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[3]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"PERSISTENCE SHIELD:\n"
"\t\t\tThis enemy is protected by an Energy Shield. Hacking, Mind Control, Teleportation, Boarding Drones, and all hull-damaging or ion weapons will all be blocked until disabled.\n"
"\t\t\tThis specific shield also increased shield recharge rate, and the enemy is capable of regenerating their Energy Shield once!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:734
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[4]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CALIBRATOR:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's weapons have +10% accuracy and 4% increased fire rate."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:741
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[5]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"CHOKING F.I.N.E.:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew take 0.75x suffocation damage.\n"
"\t\t\tWhile suffocating, they move, sabotage, repair and fight 1.5x better. Suffocation immune can't suffocate."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:750
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[6]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ARROGANCE SHIELD:\n"
"\t\t\tThis enemy is protected by an Energy Shield. Hacking, Mind Control, Teleportation, Boarding Drones, and all hull-damaging or ion weapons will all be blocked until disabled.\n"
"\t\t\tThis specific shield also makes shield recharge and  weapon charge worse, but heals friendly drones and damages enemy drones."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:758
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[7]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DREAD DECK:\n"
"\t\t\tEnemies invading this ship take 1.7x damage from everything.\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew have 2.5x healing from most sources, 2x cloning speed, and lose no skills from cloning.\n"
"\t\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: All crew in the same room as any of this ship's crew has 0.5x healing (does not stack) and cannot be cloned![[/style]] [This debuff is purple smoke]"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:768
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[8]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"PUNK HARMONY:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's Engis are more resistant and immune to Mind Control.\n"
"\t\t\tThey're also exponentially better at repairs, faster and stronger for each active level of Hacking and Mind Control on their ship!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:777
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[9]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DEFENSE KITS:\n"
"\t\t\tOn their ship, this ship's crew resist combat damage, repair and move faster, and heal over time if they are idle (and not manning)."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:784
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[10]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"DEMICLONERS:\n"
"\t\t\tDark energies try to resurrect this ship's crew if they die (not in events) without a real Clonebay.\n"
"\t\t\tAt best, they become their own lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.) If no lesser version exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:793
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[11]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"PLASMA TELEPORTER:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship can instantly set its enemy on fire when a fight starts!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:800
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[12]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SCORCH PRE-IGNITER:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's weapons are made immediately available after an FTL jump but they light a fire in the Weapons room every time they shoot a projectile or beam!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:807
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[13]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"SCORCHED EARTH:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew resists fire, and heals while extinguishing."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:814
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[14]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"BLAZING EARTH:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew resists fire, is boosted in it and generates O2 in fire, and heals while extinguishing."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:821
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[15]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"ERUPTING EARTH:\n"
"\t\t\tThis ship's crew resists fire, is boosted in it and generates much O2 in fire, and heals while extinguishing."

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:828
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[16]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FLAMMABILIZER-I:\n"
"\t\t\tYour crew's fire immunity, resistance or direct healing from fire (not extinguishing) are removed! Your crew also move slower in fire, even more for each active level of Life Support (O2) on this ship!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:835
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[17]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"FLAMMABILIZER-D:\n"
"\t\t\tYour crew takes more fire damage and move slower in fire. These effects are stronger for each active level of Life Support (O2) on this ship!"

#: src-en/data/hyperspace.xml.append:842
msgid ""
"data/hyperspace.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/mod:findLike[3]/mod:findLike[18]/mod-"
"append:shipIcon/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"WEAPONS ON FIRE:\n"
"\t\t\tThe fire rate of this ship's Weapons and Artilleries is improved by 25%. It gains an extra 1% fire rate every time they shoot a projectile or beam (up to 10%), but at the same time there's a 10% chance to light a fire in the Weapon Control and any Artillery rooms.\n"
"\t\t\tCOMBO: Scorch Preigniter increases max extra bonus to 20%."

